channel.title: Robgob's Cheat Client [BETA]
channel.description:
[center][size=1]If this is int the Wrong section, please move it [/size][/center][center]If this is not allowed please remove it
[/center][center]Alright So this is the Second official release of my cheat client. As I've said, it's currently in the BETA stage, I'm working on and adding new stuff to it still. But this is what I got so far! :rolleyes: This client is for 317's - Mostly for delta and czar based servers. But any 317 will do i guess
[size=16pt][b]::Features::[/b][/size] [/center][center][/color] [ul][li]Change Server settings! (IP, port, UID, is delta)[/li][li]Shows the names of players above their heads![/li][li]Shows the Npc ID's above the Npc's head![/li][li]Trade, Duel, Attack, and Follow yourself![/li][li]Open bank anywhere![/li][li]Bank all items in inv at once! (::bankall)[/li][li]Change chat colors, in chatarea and text effect![/li][li]Noclip![/li][li]Go Invisible![/li][li]Change into a Go-Cart![/li][li]Set a custom Look![/li][li]Open up interfaces![/li][li]Telekinetic Grab on non existing items! (Requires runes)[/li][li]Alche a non existing item! (Requires Runes)[/li][li]Check Item values anywhere![/li][li]Buy any item! - Not working[/li][li]Spawn Objects![/li][li]Attack yourself! (With or without magic)[/li][li]Attack Npcs! (With(requires runes) or without magic)[/li][li][/l][/l][/center][center]
I'll be adding more soon!
[size=16pt][b]::Pictures::[/b][/size] [img]http://i56.tinypic.com/28asv2s.jpg[/img] [img]http://i54.tinypic.com/2ptt08o.jpg[/img] [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/35kpvea.jpg[/img] [img]http://i54.tinypic.com/23ro1oo.jpg[/img] [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/sean1i.jpg[/img] [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/2dsqq2c.jpg[/img] [img]http://i53.tinypic.com/21q1.jpg[/img]
I used Galkon's client as a base and went from there. I really hope you all like the client, PLEASE SEND ME FEED BACK ON THIS!!! I want to add as many features as possible! :]So feel free to post your suggestions!
[size=4][b]Download: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?k9dlev8pcl8zcoy]Cheatz.rar[/url][/b][/size] And If I don't get any replies I'll remove this! >:l[/ul]
